  "prompt": "Do any of the Indian banks provide personalized gift cards where I can put a personalized image on the card?",
  "response": "Yes, several Indian banks offer personalized gift cards where you can add a personalized image or message. Here are some examples:\n\n1. **HDFC Bank** \u2013 HDFC Bank provides **MyCards**, which allow customers to personalize gift cards with their own images, messages, or designs. These cards can be used for gifting and are available in both physical and digital formats.\n\n2. **ICICI Bank** \u2013 ICICI Bank offers **Personalized Gift Cards** where you can upload a custom image or choose from predefined designs. These cards are available for both personal and corporate gifting purposes.\n\n3. **Axis Bank** \u2013 Axis Bank provides **GiftEdge** cards, which allow customization with personal photos, messages, or logos. These cards can be used at various retail outlets and online platforms.\n\n4. **State Bank of India (SBI)** \u2013 SBI offers **Gift Cards** with customization options, including the ability to add personalized messages or images.\n\n5. **Kotak Mahindra Bank** \u2013 Kotak Mahindra Bank provides **Kotak Gift Cards** that can be personalized with custom images, designs, or messages.\n\n### How to Get Personalized Gift Cards:\n- **Online Platforms**: Most banks allow you to create and customize gift cards through their official websites or mobile apps.\n- **Branches**: You can visit your nearest bank branch to inquire about personalized gift card options.\n- **Third-Party Providers**: Some banks partner with third-party platforms (like QwikCilver, GyFTR, etc.) to offer customized gift cards.\n\n### Features to Look For:\n- **Custom Image Upload**: Check if the bank supports image uploads for the card design.\n- **Message Customization**: Look for options to add personalized messages.\n- **Reloadable or Preloaded**: Decide if you want a reloadable or fixed-value gift card.\n- **Validity**: Confirm the card\u2019s validity period and usage terms.\n\nBefore proceeding, it\u2019s advisable to check the specific terms and conditions of the bank\u2019s gift card program to ensure it meets your requirements.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
